msgid "Return to The Essex County Express"
msgstr "重返疯狂列车"

msgid "Scenario III: Return to The Essex County Express"
msgstr "冒险III：重返疯狂列车"

msgid "Remove Agenda 1a - \"A Tear in Reality,\" from the game and replace it with the new Agenda 0a - \"Where There's Smoke\" and the new agenda 1a - \"A Tear in Reality (v.II).\" (When you construct the agenda deck, agenda 0a should be on top.)"
msgstr "将密谋1a - “现实的裂口”移出游戏，并以新的密谋0a - “无火不生烟”和新的密谋1a - “现实的裂口(版本二)”代替。(在构建密谋牌堆时，密谋0a应该在牌堆最上面)。"

msgid "Put one of the four Engine Car locations into play at random. Remove the other three versions of Engine Car from the game. Then, put six of the ten Train Car locations into play at random, in a straight line to the left of the Engine Car. Remove the remaining four Train Car locations from the game."
msgstr "在4张车头中，随机选择一张放置入场，将另外3张同名卡牌移出游戏。然后，将10张车厢卡混洗后，随机移除4张，剩余6张排成一直线放在车头左边。"

msgid "Set the Engineer story asset and all 4 copies of Across Space and Time aside, out of play."
msgstr "将机工师故事支援卡和4张跨越时空放在一边，位于场外。"
